{"tid":1103023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潤雄：小學及中學未來幾年接收更多跨境學童","createTime":"2019-04-12T06:46:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T08:27:49.000Z","uid":137217,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6929f7cffe3996f765a7aded10a4bc84298fc894","tid":1103023,"uid":137217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:46:12.000Z","msg":"在立法會特別財委會上，議會陣線范國威關注近年跨境小學生人數增加，並由北區、元朗、屯門，擴展至東涌、荃灣、葵青等地，要求當局釐清原因。教育局長楊潤雄解釋，隨住2013年實施「零雙非」政策，跨境幼稚園學童數目未來幾年會逐漸下跌，因此幼稚園即將面對整體適齡學童減少的問題，相反小學及中學未來幾年，會接收更多跨境學童，但他相信中學有足夠能力，吸納額外新增人口，當局會逐區審視人口增幅，按情況在不同的校網增加班數。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全面繼續赤化<br />\n唔怪之e家啲中學雞講埋啲垃圾國語啦<br />\n嚟緊仲多仆你個街"},{"pid":"ddb8ee85d8a70489332323a10b4be0908f4c6ea7","tid":1103023,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:47:23.000Z","msg":"Cls<br />\n依家d中學生個個講普通話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e40610577b17f4eb1c7a5cee025ecb8897c706","tid":1103023,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:48:50.000Z","msg":"屌你老母真係"},{"pid":"2506f1ee7fb30c43ecf76152a05dc97c51902e24","tid":1103023,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:59:14.000Z","msg":"佢地都可以免費教育?"},{"pid":"b97266110287661ee6250ac587a35f46e59f594f","tid":1103023,"uid":41394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2506f1ee7fb30c43ecf76152a05dc97c51902e24","tid":1103023,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:59:14.000Z","msg":"佢地都可以免費教育?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c0954a45917703d9cba73ef4bebd561d73a6377","tid":1103023,"uid":145